/**
 * Shared Amazon Connect Lambda for Sierra PSTN and EVT transfer data flows.
 *
 * TypeScript port of sierra-connect-lambda.py. Targets the Node.js Lambda
 * runtime (nodejs20.x or later) and uses the global `fetch` API. Build it into
 * a single `index.js` with `npm run build`, then deploy with
 * `node deploy-lambda.mjs`. The bundled handler is `index.handler`.
